**Impact VPS** is the product of Subnet Labs LLC, a rapidly expanding and high performance web hosting company based in Mechanicsburg, PA. We offer OpenVZ cloud servers that can be customized to fit your needs.

**Hardware:** We use the latest hardware for our VPS nodes. Dual E5v3 Intel Processors with 128GB of DDR4 Memory, 4-6 x 1TB SSDs and a 10Gbps fiber connection to the node. 

**What is a VDR?** VDR stands for Virtual Dedicated Resources. Unlike a standard VPS package, you can split the resources you pay for into as many servers of any size you want. (Per VPS Limits [HERE](http://subnetlabs.com/billing/knowledgebase.php?action=displayarticle&amp;id=17))

Have 12GB of RAM? You can create
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 x 12GB server with 4IPs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 x 4GB servers with 1 IP each and 2 with 2 IPs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 x 6GB + 2 x 3GB servers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
The combinations are endless

You choose how you want to split up your resources. Upgrade and downgrade them at any time. Can even split them across our 3 U.S. Locations (Seattle, Dallas and NYC)


